name: BetaPro Gold Bullion -2x Daily Bear ETF
longDescription: GLDD seeks daily investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to two times (200 percent) the inverse (opposite) of the daily performance of the Solactive Gold Front Month MD Rolling Futures Index ER. GLDD is denominated in Canadian dollars. GLDD does not seek to achieve its stated investment objective over a period of time greater than one day.
